FBIS4-16259 "drsov073_m_94002" FBIS-SOV-94-073 Daily Report 14 Apr 1994 Tajikistan All Mass Festivities Banned Until Further Notice All Mass Festivities Banned Until Further Notice LD1404170494 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 1530 GMT 14 Apr 94 LD1404170494 Moscow Mayak Radio Network Russian BFN [Text] The government of Tajikistan has banned the celebration of anniversaries and other events of a mass character from 14 April until further notice. In the view of the Tajik leadership, this ban will make it possible to save considerable amounts of money and food and to reduce the obligatory slaughter of private and public livestock.
